    "Examples 4, 4.1, 5, and 5.1 based on mass points in Exudyn with contextThe examples of this section summarize results of LLM regarding mass points with springdampers and distance constraints modeled in Exudyn.",
    "Since none of the LLM could correctly solve the task posed in Sect. 4.3, in-context learning is applied from now on by prompting appropriate text, see Sect.",
